import './index.scss'

const SkillsBall = (skillsArray) => {
  const TagCloud = require('TagCloud')

  const container = '.tagcloud'
  const texts = [
    'HTML',
    'CSS',
    'JAVASCRIPT',
    'SWIFT',
    'MONGOOSE',
    'REACT',
    'PYTHON',
    'SASS',
    'DJANGO',
    'NODEJS',
    'MONGODB',
    'EXPRESS',
    'MYSQL',
    'JQUERY',
    'JAVA',
  ]
  const options = {}

  return TagCloud(container, [
    'HTML',
    'CSS',
    'JAVASCRIPT',
    'SWIFT',
    'MONGOOSE',
    'REACT',
    'PYTHON',
    'SASS',
    'DJANGO',
    'NODEJS',
    'MONGODB',
    'EXPRESS',
    'MYSQL',
    'JQUERY',
    'JAVA',
  ], options)
}

export default SkillsBall
